The '''tylas vanga''' ('''''Tylas eduardi''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Vangidae]]. It is [[monotypic]] within the genus '''''Tylas'''''.<ref name = "ITIS"/> It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Madagascar]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical dry forest]] and [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]].<ref name="iucn status 12 November 2021" />

